    <h1>just to make sure</h1>

    <div class="about-layout">
      <div class="text-content">
        <ul>
          <li>find a place where daisies grow</li>
          <li>don’t pick a daisy</li>
          <li>observe the petals</li>
          <li>repeat the phrase „he loves me, he loves me not" for each petal</li>
          <li>write down the result</li>
          <li>stop when their petals close</li>
          <li>(you can bet on the outcome)</li>
        </ul>
